"1/2 cup light sour cream","3 tablespoons reduced-fat mayonnaise","1 1/2 tablespoons white balsamic vinegar","1 teaspoon sugar","1/2 teaspoon black pepper","1/4 teaspoon salt","2 cups unpeeled chopped Rome apple (about 1 medium)","1 cup golden raisins","1  (16-ounce) package cabbage-and-carrot coleslaw"